ActNational Energy Board Act Part VI (Oil and Gas) Regulations
National Energy Board Act
SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-337 - Pacific NorthWest LNG Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-337 by the National Energy Board to Pacific NorthWest LNG Ltd. as General Partner of Pacific NorthWest LNG Limited Parnership to export natural gas in the form of liquefied natural gas at the outlet of the loading arm of the liquefaction terminal to be located on Lelu Island within the Districk of Port Edward, on Federal land administered by the Prince Rupert Port Authority, British Columbia.
